txt.en: 'I am glad you have found four captives and brought them to safety. Thank you my friend.'
Duinhir can be found near Cair Andros.\n\nYou should speak to Duinhir.
Maushlak, an Uruk cook, is holding captives to vie for power at Cair Andros.\n\nYou should defeat Maushlak.
Captives are being held at Cair Andros.\n\nYou should rescue the captives.
Talk to Duinhir near Cair Andros
Leading a band of Gondorians, Duinhir, lord of Blackroot Vale, has been tasked with the retaking of Cair Andros.

'Before Damrod left, he spoke to me about Cair Andros. As you may know, it was forcefully taken before the Battle of the Pelennor. Some of the Gondorians who dwelled there, who were not slain, may be held captive. Damrod believes this to be true. While he was patrolling close to the fortress, he heard the crying of a child! We must find anyone still alive in Cair Andros and free them!'
